Dialogue: 5,0:07:57.62,0:08:00.33,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1919,1079)\1a&H80&\be2\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(199.5,97.5,199.5,-85.5,2260,2760)}Mola
